    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>When use CMS GC in jdk1.8 will appeare this error, i change the G1 Gc solve this problem.</p>\n\n<pre><code> -Xss512k -Xms6g -Xmx6g -XX:+UseG1GC -XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200 -XX:InitiatingHeapOccupancyPercent=70 -XX:NewRatio=1 -XX:SurvivorRatio=6 -XX:G1ReservePercent=10 -XX:G1HeapRegionSize=32m -XX:ConcGCThreads=6 -Xloggc:gc.log -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError -XX:+PrintGC -XX:+PrintGCDetails -XX:+PrintGCTimeStamps \n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
