      "body" : "I&#39;m not sure, but I think both answers are true - looks to me like what you are talking about is a <code>Full GC (Allocation Failure)</code>, and what the other answer is referring to is a <code>GC (Allocation Failure)</code> (notice the <code>Full</code> in the first one).  Couldn&#39;t find any solid references to this, so if someone can that would be amazing."
